---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import irp from '../assets/images/irp.webp'
import students from '../assets/images/students.webp'
import employment from '../assets/images/employment.webp'
---

<section class='py-xl relative bg-cream'>
    <div class='max-w-container-max mx-auto px-gutter'>
        <div class='text-center mb-16'>
            <h2 class='font-headline-lg text-4xl text-secondary mb-4'>
                Beneficios Exclusivos
            </h2>
            <div
                class='w-24 h-1.5 bg-primary-container mx-auto rounded-full mb-6'>
            </div>
            <p class='font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto'>
                Te acompañamos desde el primer día para que tu única
                preocupación sea disfrutar de la experiencia. Nos encargamos de
                la logística pesada por ti.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8'>
            <div
                class='group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-surface-container shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500'>
                <div class='aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden'>
                    <Image
                        class='w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110'
                        src={irp}
                        alt='Dublin image'
                    />
                    <div
                        class='absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/90 via-secondary/20 to-transparent opacity-80'>
                    </div>
                    <div class='absolute top-6 left-6 flex items-center gap-2'>
                        <div
                            class='glass-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary'>
                            100% incluido
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class='absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 text-white'>
                        <div
                            class='w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-lg'>
                            <span
                                class='material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container'
                                >assignment_turned_in</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class='text-2xl font-headline-md mb-2'>
                            Geatión de visa e IRP sin estrés
                        </h3>
                        <p class='text-sm opacity-90 line-clamp-2'>
                            Asesoría completa y acompañamiento paso a paso para
                            la apertura de tu cuenta bancaria y la cita del IRP
                            (Irish Residence Permit). Nos aseguramos de que tu
                            estatus legal esté al día sin complicaciones
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='p-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-surface'>
                    <div class='text-on-primary font-bold font-headline-md'>
                        Soporte 24/7
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary font-black text-xl'>Incluido</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class='group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-surface-container shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500'>
                <div class='aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden'>
                    <Image
                        class='w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110'
                        src={employment}
                        alt='Dublin image'
                    />
                    <div
                        class='absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/90 via-secondary/20 to-transparent opacity-80'>
                    </div>
                    <div class='absolute top-6 left-6'>
                        <div
                            class='glass-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary'>
                            Soporte local
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class='absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 text-white'>
                        <div
                            class='w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-lg'>
                            <span
                                class='material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container'
                                >work</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class='text-2xl font-headline-md mb-2'>
                            Programa de empleabilidad local
                        </h3>
                        <p class='text-sm opacity-90 line-clamp-2'>
                            Talleres intensivos para adaptar tu CV al formato
                            irlandés, preparación para entrevistas de trabajo
                            reales y acceso directo a nuestra red de contactos
                            con empresas locales en Dublín y Drogheda
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='p-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-surface'>
                    <div class='text-on-primary font-bold font-headline-md'>
                        Red de Empleo
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary font-black text-xl'>Acceso</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div
                class='group relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden bg-surface-container shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500'>
                <div class='aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden'>
                    <Image
                        class='w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110'
                        src={students}
                        alt='Dublin image'
                    />
                    <div
                        class='absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/90 via-secondary/20 to-transparent opacity-80'>
                    </div>
                    <div class='absolute top-6 left-6'>
                        <div
                            class='glass-light px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-secondary'>
                            Calidad Europea
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class='absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 text-white'>
                        <div
                            class='w-12 h-12 bg-primary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 shadow-lg'>
                            <span
                                class='material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container'
                                >translate</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <h3 class='text-2xl font-headline-md mb-2'>
                            Escuela premium certificada
                        </h3>
                        <p class='text-sm opacity-90 line-clamp-2'>
                            Grarantía de educición Europea de alta calidad para
                            tu aprendizaje.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='p-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-surface'>
                    <div class='text-on-primary font-bold font-headline-md'>
                        Todos Niveles
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary font-black text-xl'>Top Edu</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
